name: libtensorflow_cc
raw_recipe:
# This file created by conda-build 3.18.9
# ------------------------------------------------

package:
    name: libtensorflow_cc
    version: 1.13.2
source:
    fn: tensorflow-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    patches:
        - patches/0001-add-rt-to-linkopts.patch
        - patches/0002-stable-image-rotate-test.patch
        - patches/0003-relax-tolerence-in-special_math_test.patch
        - patches/0004-skip-read-only-debugger_cli_common-test.patch
        - patches/0005-fix-lookup_ops-test.patch
        - patches/0006-relax-precision-in-matrix_log_op_test.patch
        - patches/unbundle_llvm.patch
    sha256: abe3bf0c47845a628b7df4c57646f41a10ee70f914f1b018a5c761be75e1f1a9
    url: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/archive/v1.13.2.tar.gz
build:
    number: 0
    string: hf9e2511_0
requirements:
    build:
        - binutils_impl_linux-64 2.28.1 had2808c_3
        - binutils_linux-64 5.4.0 had2808c_24
        - gcc_impl_linux-64 5.4.0 habb00fd_3
        - gcc_linux-64 5.4.0 h98af8de_24
        - gxx_impl_linux-64 5.4.0 hdf63c60_3
        - gxx_linux-64 5.4.0 h98af8de_24
        - libstdcxx-ng 9.1.0 hdf63c60_0
    host:
        - _libgcc_mutex 0.1 main
        - ca-certificates 2019.9.11 hecc5488_0
        - krb5 1.16.3 h05b26f9_1001
        - libcurl 7.64.1 hda55be3_0
        - libedit 3.1.20170329 hf8c457e_1001
        - libgcc-ng 9.1.0 hdf63c60_0
        - libssh2 1.8.2 h22169c7_2
        - libstdcxx-ng 9.1.0 hdf63c60_0
        - ncurses 6.1 hf484d3e_1002
        - openssl 1.1.1c h516909a_0
        - tk 8.6.9 hed695b0_1003
        - zlib 1.2.11 h516909a_1006
    run:
        - libcurl >=7.64.1,<8.0a0
        - libgcc-ng >=5.4.0
        - libprotobuf >=3.6.1,<3.7
        - libstdcxx-ng >=5.4.0
        - nsync
        - zlib >=1.2.11,<1.3.0a0
test:
    commands:
        - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libtensorflow_cc.so
        - $CXX -std=c++11 -o test_cc -L${PREFIX}/lib/ -ltensorflow_cc -ltensorflow_framework
            -lrt -I${PREFIX}/include/ test_cc.cc && ./test_cc
    files:
        - test_cc.cc
    requires:
        - gxx_linux-64 5.4.*
about:
    description: 'TensorFlow provides multiple APIs.The lowest level API, TensorFlow
        Core

        provides you with complete programming control.

        Base package contains only tensorflow, not tensorflow-tensorboard.

        '
    dev_url: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow
    doc_source_url: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/docs_src
    doc_url: https://www.tensorflow.org/get_started/get_started
    home: http://tensorflow.org/
    license: Apache 2.0
    license_family: Apache
    license_file: LICENSE
    summary: TensorFlow is an open source machine learning framework for everyone.
extra:
    copy_test_source_files: true
    final: true
